    <summary><span data-ttu-id="8ebae-101">表示服务或客户端应用程序中的通信错误。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8ebae-101">Represents a communication error in either the service or client application.</span></span></summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="8ebae-102">可靠的客户端和服务 Windows Communication Foundation （WCF）应用程序处理在通信过程中可能引发的 <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> 对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8ebae-102">Robust client and service Windows Communication Foundation (WCF) applications handle <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> objects that may be thrown during communication.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8ebae-103">有两个客户端通常也会预计到的 <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> 派生的异常类型（<xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException%601> 和 <xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException>）。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8ebae-103">There are also two <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException>-derived exception types (<xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException%601> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException>) that clients also often expect.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8ebae-104">因此，为了防止一般 <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> 处理程序捕获到这些更具体的异常类型，请在处理 <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> 之前捕获这些异常。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8ebae-104">Therefore, in order to prevent the generic <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> handler from catching these more specific exception types, catch these exceptions prior to handling <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException>.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="8ebae-105">当接收到操作协定中指定的 SOAP 错误以响应双向操作（即，具有 <xref:System.ServiceModel.OperationContractAttribute.IsOneWay%2A> 设置为 `false`的 <xref:System.ServiceModel.OperationContractAttribute> 属性的方法）时，将在客户端上引发 <xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException%601> 对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8ebae-105"><xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException%601> objects are thrown on the client when a SOAP fault that is specified in the operation contract is received in response to a two-way operation (that is, a method with an <xref:System.ServiceModel.OperationContractAttribute> attribute with <xref:System.ServiceModel.OperationContractAttribute.IsOneWay%2A> set to `false`).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="8ebae-106">当侦听器接收到操作协定中不需要或未指定的 SOAP 错误时，将引发 <xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException> 对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8ebae-106"><xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException> objects are thrown when a listener receives a SOAP fault that is not expected or specified in the operation contract.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8ebae-107">通常，如果在调试应用程序时将服务的 <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.IncludeExceptionDetailInFaults%2A> 属性设置为 `true`，就会发生这一情况。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8ebae-107">This usually occurs when the application is being debugged and the service has the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.IncludeExceptionDetailInFaults%2A> property set to `true`.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="8ebae-108">实现自定义通道和绑定元素时，强烈建议您的组件只引发 <xref:System.TimeoutException?displayProperty=nameWithType> 或 <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> 派生的对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8ebae-108">When implementing custom channels and binding elements, it is strongly recommended that your components throw only <xref:System.TimeoutException?displayProperty=nameWithType> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException>-derived objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8ebae-109">如果您的组件引发了此组件特定的可恢复异常，则将在 <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> 对象内包装该异常。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8ebae-109">In the case where your components throw a recoverable exception that is specific to the component, wrap that exception inside a <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> object.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="8ebae-110">有关设计和使用 WCF 故障系统的详细信息，请参阅[在协定和服务中指定和处理错误](~/docs/framework/wcf/specifying-and-handling-faults-in-contracts-and-services.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8ebae-110">For more details about designing and using the WCF fault system, see [Specifying and Handling Faults in Contracts and Services](~/docs/framework/wcf/specifying-and-handling-faults-in-contracts-and-services.md).</span></span>  
  
> [!IMPORTANT]
>  <span data-ttu-id="8ebae-111">WCF 运行时将不会引发在其离开 WCF 运行时并输入用户代码的位置不安全的 <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8ebae-111">The WCF Runtime will not throw a <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> that is unsafe to handle at the point where it leaves the WCF Runtime and enters user code.</span></span>  
  
   
  
